description:
Social media-star-turned-boxer Jake Paul is set to fight Anderson Silva on October 29, 2022 at Gila River Arena in Phoenix, Arizona.

If Jake Paul wins his scheduled bout with Anderson Silva, this market will resolve to "Jake Paul". If Anderson Silva wins his scheduled bout with Jake Paul, this market will resolve to "Anderson Silva". 

If this fight ends in a draw, is not officially designated as a win for either Jake Paul or Anderson Silva, is cancelled, or otherwise is not decided by or moved to a date after November 5, 2022, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve to 50-50. This market may not resolve before October 29, 2022.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official reporting from the live boxing match between Jake Paul and Anderson Silva, however a consensus of credible reporting may be used.
